cast.overview: When single mom Callie and her two kids Trevor and Phoebe arrive in a small Oklahoma town, they begin to discover their connection to the original Ghostbusters and the secret legacy their grandfather left behind.
cast.title: Ghostbusters: Afterlife

details.biography: Emma Portner (11 November 1994) is a Canadian professional dancer and choreographer. She created the choreography for Bat Out Of Hell The Musical, Justin Bieber's music video Life Is Worth Living and several ones for her own dance company Emma Portner And Artists.
details.name: Emma Portner
